        <label xlink:type="resource" xlink:label="debiitAccount_lbl" xlink:role="http://www.xbrl.org/2003/role/documentation" xml:lang="en">Tuple: parent container for debit account numbers and identifiers. No entry is made here, but each detail line may have multiple accounts assigned to it for reporting in different GAAPs, offsetting accounts in Japan, passing along information to consolidation systems about local versus consolidating accounts, etc. For example, the account 4783HG-QOWI-192837-1000 may be expressed so: 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountMainID 1000 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountMainDescription Cash 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountSub/debiitAccountSubID 4783HG 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountSub/debiitAccountSubDescription Department 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountSub/debiitAccountSubID QOWI 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountSub/debiitAccountSubDescription Branch 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountSub/debiitAccountSubID 192837 
/debiitAccount/debiitAccountSub/debiitAccountSubDescription Division 
        </label>
        <label xlink:type="resource" xlink:label="debiitAccount_lbl" xlink:role="http://www.xbrl.org/2003/role/label" xlink:title="gl-jpn_debiitAccount_en" xml:lang="en">Debit Account Identifier</label>
